data.description:
Save hundreds of dollars on your monthly payment as this home has an assumable mortgage at 2.75%! Discover the ideal lifestyle at Magnolia Lakes! This 3-bed, 2-bath, 2-car garage home offers comfort and convenience. The eat-in kitchen opens to a spacious living room with vaulted ceilings. Enjoy a fenced backyard and screened patio. Community perks include a pool and basketball court. Conveniently located near I-95, shopping, restaurants, and 15 minutes from the beaches.

New roof (2022), new HVAC (2021) and an added bonus- a VA mortgage assumable at 2.75% interest rate. Buyer must have VA entitlement. Don't miss out on this opportunity for a home that combines comfort, convenience, and a great financing solution!
